              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18193455256401042861">Shocking in its predictions - a machine that runs everything and asks only that you live through it - even to blocking out the sun and any other stimuli that might place you outside of the control of the prescribed focus of virtual design (sound familiar)? </span>

          </span>
